### POST example with json body
POST /api/v1/users HTTP/1.1
Host: example.com
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": ""
}

### example with cookies
GET /api/v1/profile HTTP/1.1
Host: example.com
Cookie: sessionId=abc123; theme=light








